CREATE TABLE dbo.TMP_TICKET_GROUPED( TICKETID INT PRIMARY KEY, SUM_EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT FLOAT, SUM_EXTENDED_AMOUNT FLOAT, SUM_RETOUR_EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT FLOAT, SUM_RETOUR_EXTENDED_AMOUNT FLOAT, SUM_INITIAL_BALANCE FLOAT, JSON_PRODUCT NVARCHAR(MAX), JSON_RETOUR NVARCHAR(MAX) )

DECLARE @FROM_DT AS DATETIME DECLARE @UNTIL_DT AS DATETIME
SELECT @FROM_DT = CONVERT(DATETIME, VALUE, 21) FROM dbo.SETTINGS_INTEGRATION WHERE NAME = 'DIGITALTICKET' AND MODULENAME = 'SQLTASK'

INSERT INTO dbo.TMP_TICKET_GROUPED(TICKETID) SELECT dt.ID FROM dbo.TMP_DIGITALTICKET_PREPARE ue with (nolock) INNER JOIN DATA_TICKETS dt with (nolock) on dt.CUSTOMERID = ue.CUSTOMERID WHERE dt.CREATED_DT < @UNTIL_DT and dt.CREATED_DT > @FROM_DT GROUP BY dt.ID

;WITH ORDERLINES (TICKETID, EXTENDED_AMOUNT, EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT) AS ( SELECT tmp.TICKETID , SUM(dto.EXTENDED_AMOUNT) AS EXTENDED_AMOUNT , SUM(dto.EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT) AS EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT FROM dbo.TMP_TICKET_GROUPED tmp INNER JOIN dbo.DATA_TICKETS_ORDERLINES dto WITH(NOLOCK) ON tmp.TICKETID = dto.TICKETID group by tmp.TICKETID ), ORDERRETOURS (TICKETID, RETOUR_EXTENDED_AMOUNT, RETOUR_EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT) AS ( SELECT tmp.TICKETID , SUM(dtr.EXTENDED_AMOUNT) AS RETOUR_EXTENDED_AMOUNT , SUM(dtr.EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT) AS RETOUR_EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT FROM dbo.TMP_TICKET_GROUPED tmp INNER JOIN DATA_TICKETS_ORDERRETOURS dtr WITH(NOLOCK) ON tmp.TICKETID = dtr.TICKETID group by tmp.TICKETID ), GIFTCARDS (TICKETID, INTIAL_BALANCE) AS ( SELECT tmp.TICKETID , SUM(dtg.INITIAL_BALANCE) AS INTIAL_BALANCE FROM dbo.TMP_TICKET_GROUPED tmp INNER JOIN DATA_TICKETS_GIFTCARDS dtg WITH(NOLOCK) ON dtg.TICKETID = tmp.TICKETID group by tmp.TICKETID ), cte AS ( SELECT DT.TICKETID , ORL.EXTENDED_AMOUNT , ORL.EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT , ORR.RETOUR_EXTENDED_AMOUNT , ORR.RETOUR_EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT , ORG.INTIAL_BALANCE FROM TMP_TICKET_GROUPED DT LEFT JOIN ORDERLINES ORL ON ORL.TICKETID = DT.TICKETID LEFT JOIN ORDERRETOURS ORR ON DT.TICKETID = ORR.TICKETID LEFT JOIN GIFTCARDS ORG ON DT.TICKETID = ORG.TICKETID ) UPDATE tmp SET SUM_EXTENDED_AMOUNT = cte.EXTENDED_AMOUNT , SUM_EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT = cte.EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT , SUM_RETOUR_EXTENDED_AMOUNT = cte.RETOUR_EXTENDED_AMOUNT , SUM_RETOUR_EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT = cte.RETOUR_EXTENDED_DISCOUNTAMOUNT , SUM_INITIAL_BALANCE = cte.INTIAL_BALANCE FROM dbo.TMP_TICKET_GROUPED tmp INNER JOIN cte ON cte.TICKETID = tmp.TICKETID
